        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "It was in the heart of David my father — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "In his desire and purpose, as this and the like phrase is often used. ",
        "children": []
      },
