        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Thou didst well that it was in thine heart — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Thy intention and affection were well pleasing to me, although I did not permit thee, for wise reasons, to put thy pious designs into execution. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "The Lord hath performed his word ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— He concludes, as he began, with a thankful acknowledgment of God’s goodness in fulfilling his promise.",
